Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:31.68,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,As far back as I could remember, \Npeople always said the same things about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:34.31,flashback,TOWNIE A,0,0,0,,Trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:35.76,flashback,TOWNIE B,0,0,0,,Good for nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.76,0:00:36.76,flashback,TOWNIE C,0,0,0,,Useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:41.43,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I was born and raised in the slums.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:46.16,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,My parents had neither the \Nresources nor desire to feed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:56.91,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,When I got hungry, I stole, and I took.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:00:59.44,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Aside from killing, I'd do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:06.85,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I slept when I wanted to,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:09.68,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,and woke when I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:16.09,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I was free.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:19.13,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:21.77,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Hey, watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:22.85,flashback,SAMURAI A,0,0,0,,A street urchin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:24.08,flashback,SAMURAI A,0,0,0,,Trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:34.86,flashback,SAMURAI A,0,0,0,,Please, no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:42.52,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.48,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:27.68,sign_4600_15_The_Death_Row_Co,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(486,432)\pos(510,308)}Student and Master
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:33.23,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,We won't find a current leading off \Nthe island wandering the beach aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:36.00,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,The sun and sand will just exhaust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.98,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Stop being right all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.73,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,It's the best idea that an idiot \Nlike me is gonna come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.48,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,There are bugs and monsters in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:45.48,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,We could defeat them by working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:48.87,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Now that I know you're a woman, \NI'd like to avoid danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.10,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,You know what? I really \Ndo want to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.75,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,It's way too soon for \Nthat in lots of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:57.39,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,We need to leave this place alive \Nbefore we start thinking about marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:04:00.12,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Let's play it safe, even if it takes longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:02.26,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,We'll avoid fighting as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.76,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Your prudence will make you a good husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:07.89,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:15.15,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,What? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.15,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,She just fell from the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:21.40,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,The forest was... noisy. It was unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.30,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,I saw the corpses of many Soshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.58,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,Also unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.66,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,Did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.66,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,It turned into a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.04,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,It's a monster. We should run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.04,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,Why do you flee?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:40.92,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:42.80,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,It's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.06,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,Not that it matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:58.06,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,but doesn't it bother you \Nwhen things aren't as they normally are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.36,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,I don't like it, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:13.66,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,Huh, you move well for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.68,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,You're fast for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:32.93,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Nurugai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.56,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,We'll run on my signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.29,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Don't think about defeating it. Just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:38.69,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:41.09,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,I don't have much stamina, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.04,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,I take pride in the quickness of my blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:58.17,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:01.42,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.96,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,You tore my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.03,main,ZHU JIN (M),0,0,0,,How awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:39.92,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:42.54,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.75,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.92,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Run, Tenza!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.76,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:54.14,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.52,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Yamada Asaemon Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.24,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,My master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:00.64,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,He's blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:03.27,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,But he's running through \Nthe forest regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.90,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,He apparently "sees" using smells and sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.04,main,SHION,0,0,0,,We made it pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.08,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Nurugai-ku—I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.04,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Nurugai-san, now that this \Nguy's here, we'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:25.04,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,After all, I owe Shion-san my life, \Nand he taught me to use a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:25.04,sign_8551_58_Tameshi_itto_ryu,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord4\pos(430,190)\fscx75\fad(443,1)}Tameshi-itto-ryu Rank 4\N Yamada Asaemon \NShion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.30,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,He's incredible—ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:31.76,main,SHION,0,0,0,,You were relying too much on your speed, \Nand your movements were sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.68,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Go for the head or feet first against \Nan opponent like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.14,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I could hear how lukewarm \Nyour lunges were, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.14,top,TENZA,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.32,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Each strike should be executed carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.32,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:42.76,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Not even these circumstances can stop \Nyou from acting like my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:45.00,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,I'm actually kind of relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.57,main,SHION,0,0,0,,You still finish as weakly as ever, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:50.81,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:53.25,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I thought the last time \NI saw you would be on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.82,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Do you want me to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:08:00.27,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Master. What have \Nyou been doing all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:05.71,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I completed my duty and was on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.15,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Unable to find a current \Nleading away from the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:18.04,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I kept searching for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.60,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:24.23,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I found what seemed to be a current \Nleading out in just one place, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:29.07,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I heard a noise and detected a presence \Nlike nothing I'd experienced before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:32.95,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Realizing there were limits to what \Na blind man could accomplish alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.99,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I searched for others \Nwho were also heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.10,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Please take us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.28,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Together, the three of us \Ncan figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:42.62,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.24,main,SHION,0,0,0,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.94,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.13,main,SHION,0,0,0,,It's your turn to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.88,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Why are you protecting a criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.64,main,SHION,0,0,0,,You were told to execute \Ncriminals immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.64,main,SHION,0,0,0,,if they violated the rules \Nor the unexpected occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.14,main,SHION,0,0,0,,That's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.86,main,SHION,0,0,0,,She tried to seduce me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.36,main,SHION,0,0,0,,So I executed her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.79,main,SHION,0,0,0,,as painlessly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:22.48,main,SHION,0,0,0,,You seem to be assisting \Nthat criminal. Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.72,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Depending on your answer, \Nan execution may be in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.63,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,This child has committed no crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:32.38,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I've memorized most \Nof the contents of the roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.38,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I know the circumstances of the criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:39.76,main,SHION,0,0,0,,But the times we live in dictate \Nwhat is a crime, Tenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:44.40,main,SHION,0,0,0,,The Yamada Asaemon are \Nthe blade swung down by the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:48.12,main,SHION,0,0,0,,It would be illogical \Nfor a sword to choose who it cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:50.40,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Above all else, you violating \Nthe rules could be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.03,main,SHION,0,0,0,,interpreted as treason committed \Nby the entire Yamada clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:56.53,main,SHION,0,0,0,,The actions of a single man \Ncould threaten the entire clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:01.53,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,But you taught me how to use a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.29,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,When I was a homeless scoundrel,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:08.79,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,you took me in, even though you \Nweren't obligated to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:13.30,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Because I sensed resourcefulness \Nand potential in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.40,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Then it's the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:19.43,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,I sense there's potential in a world \Nwhere this child can live freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:22.85,main,SHION,0,0,0,,You've come to speak like a grown man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.68,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:29.47,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Besides, I know you're a kind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:32.31,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,I know you'll listen to me \Nif I speak from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.92,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,I don't get why you'd help people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.68,main,SHION,0,0,0,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:49.96,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.63,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,See? He's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.96,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.64,main,SHION,0,0,0,,But the matter has simply been tabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:11:02.09,main,SHION,0,0,0,,If protecting her would threaten \Nthe Yamada clan or you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:03.35,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.55,main,SHION,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:08.78,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Her? I'm impressed you figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:09.98,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:11.82,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I've got a good {\i1}eye{\i0} for evaluating people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.36,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,You sure do love making jokes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:17.86,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.61,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Nurugai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.70,main,SHION,0,0,0,,But you needn't call me "Master."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:26.43,main,SHION,0,0,0,,I haven't taught you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.77,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Let's not waste any time checking \Nout this current you found.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.13,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.38,main,SHION,0,0,0,,We'll take our time and be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:38.73,main,SHION,0,0,0,,The greatest threat we face \Ncurrently is that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.42,main,SHION,0,0,0,,It can't possibly be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.43,main,SHION,0,0,0,,We should consider how we'll \Nrespond if we encounter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:47.63,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,If we just intend to flee, then we \Nshould be able to do what we did earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.19,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,You underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.99,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,You saved us, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:11:59.94,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.20,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.45,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:07.45,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,I thought I'd taken off his head. Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:16.79,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,I've gotten used to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:22.89,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,You have to be alive to become Tan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.80,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,but because you're so \Nannoying, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:29.66,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,What should I do? I should run, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.31,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,No, I have to kill it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.07,main,TENZA,0,0,0,,Tameshi-itto-ryu Ultimate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.41,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Wait, Ten—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.45,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Pounding Torrent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.96,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,I told you, I'm used to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.56,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Tenza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:16.94,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Hey, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.93,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Why'd you take in a guy like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.51,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Mind your language.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.85,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Why did you take me in, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.07,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Taking lives is our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:31.28,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,I wish to spend the rest \Nof my time helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:35.21,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,It's true that you're \Na bit rough around the edges...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.83,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,but I sense potential in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.31,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you great?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.66,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,I don't get why you'd help people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.47,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.59,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,You're sloppy with your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.58,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,You're allowing your \Nemotions to control you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:58.81,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Your rage, and your doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:02.71,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,It's not like I want to be a samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:04.49,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,This is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.96,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you to follow \Nthe samurai code from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:12.12,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,But someday, if you find \Nsomething you want to protect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.87,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,the sword skills you've developed \Nwill definitely help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.62,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Something I want to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:21.63,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Look at that cherry blossom tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:24.52,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Its trunk is lean, \Nand its flowers are still buds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:28.63,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,But buds contain all manner of potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:30.89,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,So do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:35.20,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,The day will come when your \Nbuds of potential blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.57,flashbacktop,TOWNIE A,0,0,0,,Trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.32,flashbacktop,TOWNIE B,0,0,0,,Good for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:37.94,flashbacktop,TOWNIE C,0,0,0,,Useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.11,flashbacktop,SAMURAI A,0,0,0,,A street urchin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.20,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Now, continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:43.82,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.69,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,I don't have potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:50.24,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,I don't have status or money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:54.20,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Since the day I was born, \NI've never had potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.53,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,I'm quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:58.54,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.91,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,I said I'm quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:02.29,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this strict lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.52,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,I wanna live how I want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.88,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Are you serious about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:07.97,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.61,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Then I have a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:12.05,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,A condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.60,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Just one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:18.68,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Anytime, anywhere. Land a single blow on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.56,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,If you can do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:22.48,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,then I'll allow you to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.84,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.66,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Where are you going? \NThe dojo is in the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:37.29,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Shion told me about your deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.66,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Have you already landed a blow on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:42.14,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Are you going to drag me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:43.72,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:44.67,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.91,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,But before you go, accompany me on a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:50.86,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,I woke up too early and have nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.56,sign_22848_222_Official_Pardon,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&H2F2F2F&\3c&HADADAD&}Namu Amida Butsu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:06.07,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Shion's former junior sleeps here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:07.78,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,His name was Tesshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.78,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,His junior?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.61,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Like you, he was dissolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:15.82,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,He had talent, but he lacked motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:20.45,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Then Master must've put him \Nthrough the wringer, like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:26.22,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,At the time, Shion focused \Non improving his own skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:29.25,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,He didn't have nearly the same passion \Nfor teaching as he does now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:34.59,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,In the end, Tesshin said he'd live \Nhow he pleased and left the dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.60,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,For a while, things stayed the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:42.77,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,That day, Shion went out \Nto test his sword just like he always did
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:45.08,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,and stood before the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:53.24,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,But Shion wouldn't lower \Nthe sword he raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.80,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:55.72,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:17:00.49,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Shion realized the criminal \Nbefore him was Tesshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.11,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,After leaving the dojo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:07.01,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Tesshin eventually struggled \Nto feed himself and turned to crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:10.25,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,What did Master do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.76,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Naturally, he killed him \Nas a Yamada Asaemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:18.26,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Shion clearly heard Tesshin's last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.76,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Apparently, he said this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:25.02,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,"Master, I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:29.75,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,That's when Shion became passionate about
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.98,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,teaching his juniors \Nand began helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:36.59,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,If you live the life of a scoundrel, \Nyou might eventually end up the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:40.91,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,He probably felt it would be \Na waste for that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.49,flashback italics,SHION,0,0,0,,So do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:46.92,flashback italics,SHION,0,0,0,,The day will come when your \Nbuds of potential blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.00,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:51.77,flashback,EIZEN,0,0,0,,Will you run from this place \Nwithout landing a single blow on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.72,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Ah, Tenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.29,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Master, please spar with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.49,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,You seem different than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:24.37,flashback italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I've never seriously devoted myself \Nto anything before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:32.54,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Your flanks are undefended.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.55,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:38.32,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.14,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.13,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:47.18,flashback italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I want to land a blow on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:55.63,flashback italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,He's the first person \Nto believe in my potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.04,flashback italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Hey, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:01.92,flashback italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Can I believe in my own potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:05.20,flashback italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,And like you said, someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:09.05,flashback italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Someday, will I find \Nsomeone I want to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:24.51,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,My fingertips are growing cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.75,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,But I'm burning from the chest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.48,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:35.56,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:41.74,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,We're all going to be \Nkilled by this monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.71,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:59.84,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Even if I die, I'll make sure they escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.68,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I don't care how I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:05.60,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I'll do everything I can \Nto buy time for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:15.90,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:19.15,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Run. Please run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:32.56,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Both of you, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.46,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Don't, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.92,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,You can't beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.42,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.43,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,My throat's too damaged to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.66,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Master, please run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.30,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Just one word.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:47.81,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Let me speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.07,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Tenza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:23.59,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Master, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.34,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,You took care of me, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.85,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Nurugai-san, please live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:31.35,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,You have potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.24,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,Potential...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:37.75,italics,TENZA,0,0,0,,I wonder what potential I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.35,main,ZHU JIN (F),0,0,0,,He was pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:06.51,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Why are we abandoning him? I'm going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.36,main,SHION,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:11.01,main,SHION,0,0,0,,This is what Tenza wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:15.02,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,But still... you're his master, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.58,main,NURUGAI,0,0,0,,Isn't he your student?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:17.52,main,SHION,0,0,0,,He's more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:22.02,main,SHION,0,0,0,,We're brothers who wanted the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:27.53,main,SHION,0,0,0,,He risked his life for us. \NI can't waste that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:30.57,main,SHION,0,0,0,,We can't beat that monster right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.72,main,SHION,0,0,0,,If we hadn't run, we would've all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:34.54,main,SHION,0,0,0,,We had to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:38.86,main,SHION,0,0,0,,But I swear we'll make them pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:10.37,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,All right! I hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:11.82,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,That was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.02,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Now you're free to do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:22.67,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Master, will you keep \Nteaching—no, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:27.48,flashback,TENZA,0,0,0,,Master, I humbly request that you \Ncontinue teaching me to use a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:29.37,flashback,SHION,0,0,0,,Of course.
